    • Constructor Detail

      • BrailleFileFormat

        public BrailleFileFormat(org.daisy.dotify.api.embosser.FileFormat format,
                         org.daisy.dotify.api.paper.Area printableArea,
                         Dimension pageWidth,
                         Dimension pageHeight,
                         double cellWidth,
                         double cellHeight,
                         boolean sheetsMultipleOfTwo,
                         boolean blankLastPage,
                         boolean overflowAllowed,
                         Medium.MediumBuilder parser)
        printableArea, pageWidth and pageHeight determine the dimensions of the medium as observed in media queries, but may or may not be linked to hard constraints such as a physical sheet of paper and embosser.
        Parameters:
        printableArea - The dimensions and position of the printable area of the page
        sheetsMultipleOfTwo - whether volumes have a number of sheets that is a multiple of 2
        blankLastPage - whether the last page of each volume should be left blank
